    "body": "Hi @bluespore awesome that you tested Algolia, indeed this is an issue we should more proactively warn our users about.\n\nFor instance if you ask for a numericRefinementList and the underlying attribute is not an integer then you should get a clear warning (your usecase).\n\nWe have already an issue about it: #591 and we will work on this pretty soon to avoid our users to waste more time.\n\nThanks\n",
